org.nd4j.linalg.api.ops

Interface Module

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CustomOp
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseModule, Linear

    public interface Module
extends CustomOp
    A Module is a CustomOp with varying input arguments and automatically calculated outputs defined at a higher level than c++. A Module is meant to be a way of implementing custom operations in straight java/nd4j.
